{"tid":559963,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC][自組機械人競速] Break Arts II - 破壞就係藝術","createTime":"2018-02-13T16:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T14:20:28.000Z","uid":14404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"374deb7d38fe2be880901fd6f705210f9bf36dfa","tid":559963,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/547360/header.jpg?t=1518508893\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F547360%2Fheader.jpg%3Ft%3D1518508893&h=1e2746d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTrailer:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZEMaNjBhmgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZEMaNjBhmgE&d=DyFP53Hn%2F%2F%2BzStwfSKSx2xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=70aff5a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZEMaNjBhmgE</a><br />\nBreak Arts II 係日本Mercury Studio開發嘅競速game，同其他同類型game一樣要同其他玩家喺賽道鬥快爭名次，不過今次大家揸嘅唔再係車而係機械人<br />\n<br />\n隻game最大特色係玩家可以親自砌屬於自己嘅機械人，好似砌模型咁將唔同parts砌落骨架到，每件parts都會影響唔同數值<br />\n你鍾意高速/短途爆發/平均/重甲/強攻咩類型都得<br />\n<br />\n冇錯係強攻，呢隻game第二個特色就係可以比賽嘅時候攻擊人打到人爆機(當然會重生不過要時間，而某d parts係會影響重生時間長短)<br />\n機械人嘅左右手各持1把武器，當然玩家一樣可以自己砌去決定種類，傷害，填裝時間，冷卻時間等等<br />\n遠戰/近戰/陷阱流任君選擇(不過近戰同狙好難用就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SvyXdAibJVM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FSvyXdAibJVM%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=0f211ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.img2.win/gb/86/1j/cumlvys.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.img2.win%2Fgb%2F86%2F1j%2Fcumlvys.jpeg&h=eb56d62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/860604907629532973/F1648F9383E41B6DDE452336A4B70F3473219B72/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F860604907629532973%2FF1648F9383E41B6DDE452336A4B70F3473219B72%2F&h=660e8926&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/860604907626453811/7F9DBA0E53145A4959E2946F8BAAFE25196F9B20/?interpolation=lanczos-none&amp;output-format=jpeg&amp;output-quality=95&amp;fit=inside%7C1024%3A*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F860604907626453811%2F7F9DBA0E53145A4959E2946F8BAAFE25196F9B20%2F%3Finterpolation%3Dlanczos-none%26output-format%3Djpeg%26output-quality%3D95%26fit%3Dinside%257C1024%253A%2A&h=2e232b22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/860604907629540384/36AB65574925EA11E4617DDA64F909762A6E3F8D/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F860604907629540384%2F36AB65574925EA11E4617DDA64F909762A6E3F8D%2F&h=1b50b08a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/943935697849392082/578A35BE49A8046CCA2BF6CEE9E63B10505AA043/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F943935697849392082%2F578A35BE49A8046CCA2BF6CEE9E63B10505AA043%2F&h=ad86bbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteam:<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/547360/BREAK_ARTS_II/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F547360%2FBREAK_ARTS_II%2F&d=DyFP53Hn%2F%2F%2BzStwfSKSx2xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e7b7c7b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/547360/BREAK_ARTS_II/</a><br />\n對應語言: 日文/英文/繁體中文/簡體中文/韓文(旁白可以轉幾種日文男女聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"4ce4ebdf567173fa37d08a4e1410328ebadb73d9","tid":559963,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"隻game早幾日先出所以未算好完善<br />\n條賽道我自己覺得太花同冇圍欄<br />\n我呢d廢J一上手覺得好難<br />\n同好似話會有嘅共鬥raid mode仲未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgm